<ul><li><i>Burst Fire</i> is automatically learned with her first skill point upon spawning.</li>
<li>Any of <i>Burst Fire's</i> rounds hitting a champion will draw minion aggro, regardless of whether or not other targets were hit first by <i>Burst Fire's</i> rounds.
<ul><li>A lightning chain from a <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Lightning Crash" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Lightning_Crash" title="Lightning Crash"><img alt="Lightning Crash" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Lightning Crash.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Lightning_Crash.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/2/23/Zeri_Lightning_Crash.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813185746" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Lightning_Crash" title="Zeri/LoL">Lightning Crash</a></span></span> empowered <i>Burst Fire</i> will not draw minion aggro.</li></ul></li>
<li><i>Burst Fire</i> does not trigger <span class="inline-image label-after item-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-item="Tear of the Goddess" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Tear_of_the_Goddess" title="Tear of the Goddess&#39;"><img alt="Tear of the Goddess&#39;" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Tear of the Goddess item.png" data-image-key="Tear_of_the_Goddess_item.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/2/2b/Tear_of_the_Goddess_item.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20201104203628" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Tear_of_the_Goddess" title="Tear of the Goddess">Tear of the Goddess'</a></span></span> <a href="/wiki/Named_item_effect#Mana_Charge" title="Named item effect">Mana Charge</a>.</li>
<li><i>Burst Fire's</i> cooldown is not reduced by <span class="inline-image label-after item-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-item="Navori Flickerblade" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Navori_Flickerblade" title="Navori Flickerblade"><img alt="Navori Flickerblade" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Navori Flickerblade item.png" data-image-key="Navori_Flickerblade_item.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/a/a4/Navori_Flickerblade_item.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240511183703" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Navori_Flickerblade" title="Navori Flickerblade">Navori Flickerblade</a></span></span>.</li>
<li><span class="champion-ability-icon"><span class="inline-image label-after champion-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Amumu" data-skin="Original" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Amumu/LoL" title="Amumu&#39;s"><img alt="Amumu&#39;s" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Amumu OriginalSquare.png" data-image-key="Amumu_OriginalSquare.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/40/Amumu_OriginalSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20150402215322" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Amumu/LoL" title="Amumu/LoL">Amumu's</a></span></span> <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Amumu" data-ability="Tantrum" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Amumu/LoL#Tantrum" title="Tantrum&#39;s"><img alt="Tantrum&#39;s" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Amumu Tantrum.png" data-image-key="Amumu_Tantrum.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/2/2d/Amumu_Tantrum.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20210827175608" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Amumu/LoL#Tantrum" title="Amumu/LoL">Tantrum's</a></span></span></span>, <span class="champion-ability-icon"><span class="inline-image label-after champion-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Fizz" data-skin="Original" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Fizz/LoL" title="Fizz&#39;s"><img alt="Fizz&#39;s" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Fizz OriginalSquare.png" data-image-key="Fizz_OriginalSquare.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/5f/Fizz_OriginalSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20150402220015" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Fizz/LoL" title="Fizz/LoL">Fizz's</a></span></span> <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Fizz" data-ability="Nimble Fighter" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Fizz/LoL#Nimble_Fighter" title="Nimble Fighter&#39;s"><img alt="Nimble Fighter&#39;s" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Fizz Nimble Fighter.png" data-image-key="Fizz_Nimble_Fighter.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/70/Fizz_Nimble_Fighter.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240812215209" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Fizz/LoL#Nimble_Fighter" title="Fizz/LoL">Nimble Fighter's</a></span></span></span>, and <span class="champion-ability-icon"><span class="inline-image label-after champion-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Leona" data-skin="Original" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Leona/LoL" title="Leona&#39;s"><img alt="Leona&#39;s" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Leona OriginalSquare.png" data-image-key="Leona_OriginalSquare.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/b/ba/Leona_OriginalSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20150402220518" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Leona/LoL" title="Leona/LoL">Leona's</a></span></span> <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Leona" data-ability="Eclipse" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Leona/LoL#Eclipse" title="Eclipse&#39;s"><img alt="Eclipse&#39;s" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Leona Eclipse.png" data-image-key="Leona_Eclipse.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/e/ee/Leona_Eclipse.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20230830010727" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Leona/LoL#Eclipse" title="Leona/LoL">Eclipse's</a></span></span></span> flat damage reduction apply to <b>each</b> of the 7 instances of damage from <i>Burst Fire</i>.
<ul><li><span class="inline-image label-after item-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-item="Warden&#39;s Mail" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Warden%27s_Mail" title="Warden&#39;s Mail&#39;s"><img alt="Warden&#39;s Mail&#39;s" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Warden&#39;s Mail item.png" data-image-key="Warden%27s_Mail_item.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/f/ff/Warden%27s_Mail_item.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20201029211029" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Warden%27s_Mail" title="Warden&#39;s Mail">Warden's Mail's</a></span></span> flat damage reduction and cap only apply to the first instance of damage.</li>
<li><span class="inline-image label-after item-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-item="Guardian&#39;s Horn" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Guardian%27s_Horn" title="Guardian&#39;s Horn&#39;s"><img alt="Guardian&#39;s Horn&#39;s" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Guardian&#39;s Horn item.png" data-image-key="Guardian%27s_Horn_item.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/6/61/Guardian%27s_Horn_item.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20221019165449" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Guardian%27s_Horn" title="Guardian&#39;s Horn">Guardian's Horn's</a></span></span> flat damage reduction only applies to the first instance of damage, but handles it as damage-over-time (reduced to 25% effectiveness).</li></ul></li>
<li><i>Burst Fire</i> still counts as an ability activation for the purposes of on-cast effects such as triggering <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Kassadin" data-ability="Force Pulse" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Kassadin/LoL#Force_Pulse" title="Force Pulse&#39;s"><img alt="Force Pulse&#39;s" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Kassadin Force Pulse.png" data-image-key="Kassadin_Force_Pulse.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/2/22/Kassadin_Force_Pulse.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813002424" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Kassadin/LoL#Force_Pulse" title="Kassadin/LoL">Force Pulse's</a></span></span> passive.
<ul><li>It does <b>not</b> count as an ability activation for <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Spellblade"><a href="/wiki/Named_item_effect#Spellblade" title="Named item effect"><img alt="Sheen item" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Sheen item.png" data-image-key="Sheen_item.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/c/c6/Sheen_item.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20201118210052" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Named_item_effect#Spellblade" title="Named item effect">Spellblade</a></span>.</li></ul></li>
<li><i>Burst Fire</i> can hit <b>all</b> enemy units that a basic attack would be able to target. This does include <a href="/wiki/Jungle_plants" title="Jungle plants">jungle plants</a>, <a href="/wiki/Structure" class="mw-redirect" title="Structure">structures</a>, and <a href="/wiki/Ward" title="Ward">wards</a>.
<ul><li>Wards will only be hit once by <i>Burst Fire</i>. <a href="/wiki/Stealth#Stealthed_traps_and_wards" title="Stealth">Stealthed wards and traps</a> will not be hit.</li>
<li>Champion-summoned units behave differently depending on the unit.
<ul><li><i>Gangplank's</i> <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Gangplank" data-ability="Powder Keg" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Gangplank/LoL#Powder_Keg" title="Powder Keg"><img alt="Powder Keg" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Gangplank Powder Keg.png" data-image-key="Gangplank_Powder_Keg.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/4e/Gangplank_Powder_Keg.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240812215916" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Gangplank/LoL#Powder_Keg" title="Gangplank/LoL">Powder Keg</a></span></span> and <i>Yorick’s</i> <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Yorick" data-ability="Dark Procession" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Yorick/LoL#Dark_Procession" title="Dark Procession"><img alt="Dark Procession" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Yorick Dark Procession.png" data-image-key="Yorick_Dark_Procession.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/b/bd/Yorick_Dark_Procession.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813183956" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Yorick/LoL#Dark_Procession" title="Yorick/LoL">Dark Procession</a></span></span> are hit only once by <i>Burst Fire</i>, and any subsequent rounds not empowered by <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Spark Surge" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Spark_Surge" title="Spark Surge"><img alt="Spark Surge" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Spark Surge.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Spark_Surge.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/b/b7/Zeri_Spark_Surge.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813185756" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Spark_Surge" title="Zeri/LoL">Spark Surge</a></span></span> will stop upon reaching the same object.</li>
<li><i>Kalista’s</i> <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Kalista" data-ability="Sentinel" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Kalista/LoL#Sentinel" title="Sentinel"><img alt="Sentinel" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Kalista Sentinel.png" data-image-key="Kalista_Sentinel.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/b/b5/Kalista_Sentinel.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813001415" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Kalista/LoL#Sentinel" title="Kalista/LoL">Sentinel</a></span></span> is hit only once by <i>Burst Fire</i>, but any subsequent rounds will continue to travel through the <i>Sentinel</i>.</li></ul></li></ul></li>
<li>If <i>Burst Fire</i> hits an enemy while <b>Zeri</b> is not visible to enemies, the area around her (400 units) will be revealed for 4.<small>5</small> seconds.</li>
<li><i>Burst Fire</i> rolls <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Critical strike"><a href="/wiki/Critical_strike" title="Critical strike"><img alt="Critical strike icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Critical strike icon.png" data-image-key="Critical_strike_icon.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/41/Critical_strike_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20191126102550" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Critical_strike" title="Critical strike">critical strike</a></span> for all rounds as well as the additional physical damage dealt when <b>Zeri</b> is <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Lightning Crash" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Lightning_Crash" title="Overcharged"><img alt="Overcharged" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Lightning Crash.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Lightning_Crash.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/2/23/Zeri_Lightning_Crash.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813185746" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Lightning_Crash" title="Zeri/LoL">Overcharged</a></span></span>.</li>
<li><i>Burst Fire</i> is parried by <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Dodge"><a href="/wiki/Attack_effects#Parrying" title="Attack effects"><img alt="Jax Counter Strike old" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Jax Counter Strike old.png" data-image-key="Jax_Counter_Strike_old.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/6/62/Jax_Counter_Strike_old.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20171223030746" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Attack_effects#Parrying" title="Attack effects">dodge</a></span> and <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Block"><a href="/wiki/Attack_effects#Parrying" title="Attack effects"><img alt="Spirit&#39;s Refuge" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Shen Spirit&#39;s Refuge.png" data-image-key="Shen_Spirit%27s_Refuge.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/0a/Shen_Spirit%27s_Refuge.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813161041" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Attack_effects#Parrying" title="Attack effects">block</a></span>.
<ul><li><span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Blind"><a href="/wiki/Blind" title="Blind"><img alt="Blind icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Blind icon.png" data-image-key="Blind_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/8/81/Blind_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20171201224954" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Blind" class="mw-redirect" title="Blind">Blind</a></span> causes <i>Burst Fire</i> to cast in a random direction. The rounds will still deal damage to enemies hit.</li></ul></li>
<li><i>Burst Fire's</i> rounds are each fired in the target direction from where <b>Zeri</b> is at the time.</li>
<li><b>Only</b> attack speed granted by being <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Lightning Crash" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Lightning_Crash" title="Overcharged"><img alt="Overcharged" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Lightning Crash.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Lightning_Crash.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/2/23/Zeri_Lightning_Crash.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813185746" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Lightning_Crash" title="Zeri/LoL">Overcharged</a></span></span> can exceed the cap of 1.<small>5</small>.
<ul><li><span class="inline-image label-after rune-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-rune="Hail of Blades" data-game="lol"><span style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Hail_of_Blades_(Rune)" title="Hail of Blades"><img alt="Hail of Blades" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Hail of Blades rune.png" data-image-key="Hail_of_Blades_rune.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/2/2e/Hail_of_Blades_rune.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20180505140825" class="lazyload" /></a></span> <span style="word-break: keep-all;;"><a href="/wiki/Hail_of_Blades_(Rune)" class="mw-redirect" title="Hail of Blades (Rune)">Hail of Blades</a></span></span> does not allow <b>Zeri</b> to exceed her attack speed cap.</li></ul></li>
<li>Items and runes that trigger off of attacking [eg <span class="inline-image label-after rune-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-rune="Fleet Footwork" data-game="lol"><span style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Fleet_Footwork_(Rune)" title="Fleet Footwork"><img alt="Fleet Footwork" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Fleet Footwork rune.png" data-image-key="Fleet_Footwork_rune.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/46/Fleet_Footwork_rune.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20171126182047" class="lazyload" /></a></span> <span style="word-break: keep-all;;"><a href="/wiki/Fleet_Footwork_(Rune)" class="mw-redirect" title="Fleet Footwork (Rune)">Fleet Footwork</a></span></span>, <span class="inline-image label-after item-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-item="Kraken Slayer" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Kraken_Slayer" title="Kraken Slayer"><img alt="Kraken Slayer" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Kraken Slayer item.png" data-image-key="Kraken_Slayer_item.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/3/3d/Kraken_Slayer_item.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20201015163506" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Kraken_Slayer" title="Kraken Slayer">Kraken Slayer</a></span></span>] will only trigger if <i>Burst Fire</i> hits a unit.</li>
<li>If Zeri would get full <a href="/wiki/Named_item_effect#Energized" title="Named item effect">Energized</a> stacks from a <i>Burst Fire</i>, the rest of the rounds will trigger Energized.</li>
<li><i>Burst Fire's</i> cast-indicator does not show <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Range" title="Range"><img alt="Range icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="15" height="15" data-image-name="Range icon.png" data-image-key="Range_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/13/Range_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/15?cb=20170715002053" class="lazyload" /></a>&#160;range</span> increases; modified range VFX are still visible around the champion model.</li>
<li><i>Burst Fire</i> can apply the effect of <span class="inline-image label-after item-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-item="Horizon Focus" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Horizon_Focus" title="Horizon Focus"><img alt="Horizon Focus" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Horizon Focus item.png" data-image-key="Horizon_Focus_item.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/3/3b/Horizon_Focus_item.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20201118204947" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Horizon_Focus" title="Horizon Focus">Horizon Focus</a></span></span> when the enemy hit is within the last 50 units of this ability.<sup><span class="basic-tooltip" style="border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;" title="This may not be intended.">(note)</span></sup></li>
<li><i>Burst Fire</i> uses a modified icon when empowered by <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Spark Surge" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Spark_Surge" title="Spark Surge"><img alt="Spark Surge" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Spark Surge.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Spark_Surge.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/b/b7/Zeri_Spark_Surge.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813185756" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Spark_Surge" title="Zeri/LoL">Spark Surge</a></span></span> (<img alt="Zeri Burst Fire 2" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Zeri Burst Fire 2.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Burst_Fire_2.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/df/Zeri_Burst_Fire_2.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20220108011904" class="lazyload" />) and <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Lightning Crash" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Lightning_Crash" title="Lightning Crash"><img alt="Lightning Crash" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Lightning Crash.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Lightning_Crash.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/2/23/Zeri_Lightning_Crash.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813185746" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Lightning_Crash" title="Zeri/LoL">Lightning Crash</a></span></span> (<img alt="Zeri Burst Fire 3" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Zeri Burst Fire 3.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Burst_Fire_3.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/de/Zeri_Burst_Fire_3.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20220108011914" class="lazyload" />) as well as both (<img alt="Zeri Burst Fire 4" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Zeri Burst Fire 4.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Burst_Fire_4.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/c/c4/Zeri_Burst_Fire_4.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20220108011928" class="lazyload" />).</li>
<li>Destroying a ward that is targetable but not visible to <b>Zeri's</b> team (e.g. a <span class="inline-image label-after item-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-item="Control Ward" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Control_Ward" title="Control Ward"><img alt="Control Ward" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Control Ward item.png" data-image-key="Control_Ward_item.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/1b/Control_Ward_item.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20201027193925" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Control_Ward" title="Control Ward">Control Ward</a></span></span> in <a href="/wiki/Fog_of_War" class="mw-redirect" title="Fog of War">Fog of War</a>) via <i>Burst Fire</i> uniquely allows her to remove its accompanying <a href="/wiki/Ward#Ward_Timers" title="Ward">ward timer</a> (if it exists) without seeing the ward being destroyed.</li></ul>
<div style="clear:both"></div>
</div><p class="mw-empty-elt"></p></div><div class="wds-tab__content"><p class="mw-empty-elt"> 
</p><div style="display:none;"><b>Map-Specific Differences</b><br /></div>
<div style="padding:0.5em 1em;">&#32;
<dl><dt><span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Howling abyss"><a href="/wiki/Howling_Abyss_(League_of_Legends)" title="Howling Abyss (League of Legends)"><img alt="Howling Abyss icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Howling Abyss icon.png" data-image-key="Howling_Abyss_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/02/Howling_Abyss_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20171101151627" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Howling_Abyss_(League_of_Legends)" title="Howling Abyss (League of Legends)">Howling Abyss</a></span> differences <sup><a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="text" href="https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/Template:Map_changes/data/aram?action=edit">edit</a></sup></dt>
<dd></dd></dl>
<ul><li><b>Zeri</b> will start the game with one point already ranked in <i>Burst Fire!</i>, allowing her to allocate the other two to her other abilities.<div style="clear:both"></div></li></ul>
</div><p class="mw-empty-elt"></p></div></div></div>
