<ul><li><i>Spark Surge's</i> extended dash travels based on the thickness of the terrain, up to a maximum distance.</li>
<li>The following table refers for interactions while <b>Zeri</b> is dashing:</li></ul>
<table class="article-table" style="font-size:small; width:475px; padding: 1em; box-shadow: #0a1827 0px 0px 25px 15px;">

<tbody><tr>
<th colspan="2">Attacking
</th>
<td>Disabled
</td></tr>
<tr>
<th colspan="2">Abilities
</th>
