</div><div style="width:100%; display:grid; grid-template-columns: 78px 3fr 1.4fr; row-gap: 0.5em;">
<div style="text-align:center; padding:7px; vertical-align:top;"> <div style="float:left;box-shadow:black 0 2px 5px 0;width:64px"><img alt="Zeri Lightning Crash" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="64" height="64" data-image-name="Zeri Lightning Crash.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Lightning_Crash.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/2/23/Zeri_Lightning_Crash.png/revision/latest?cb=20240813185746" class="lazyload" /></div></div>
<div style="grid-column-end: span 2; display:contents">
<div style="vertical-align:top; padding: 0 0 0 7px;"><p><span class="template_sbc"><b>Active:</b></span> <b>Zeri</b> discharges an electric nova that deals <span class="ll-item navbox">Damage mitigated with Shifting Sands (E)</span><span><span style="color: #00B0F0; white-space:normal">magic damage</span></span> to nearby enemies. If this hits at least one enemy champion, she enters <i>Overcharged</i> for 5 seconds. Hitting an enemy champion with an ability or <i><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Basic Attack 2" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Basic_Attack_2" title="charged"><img alt="charged" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Living Battery 2.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Living_Battery_2.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/55/Zeri_Living_Battery_2.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20220108011853" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Basic_Attack_2" title="Zeri/LoL">charged</a></span></span></i> basic attack will extend the duration by 1.<small>5</small> seconds, up to its original duration.</p></div>
<table style="border-collapse: collapse;"><tbody><tr><td style="vertical-align:top;"><div style="padding: 0 7px"><div class="skill_leveling">
<dl class="skill-tabs"><dt><span class="template_lc"><b>Magic Damage:</b></span></dt><dd>175 / 275 / 375 <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions stunned with Pyromania (P)</span><span><span style="color:orange; white-space:normal">(+ 85% <b>bonus</b> AD)</span></span> <span class="ll-item navbox">Multiple champions hit with Between Worlds (R)</span><span><span style="color: #7A6DFF; white-space:normal">(+ 110% AP)</span></span></dd></dl></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div style="text-align:center; padding:7px; vertical-align:top;">&#32;</div>
<div style="grid-column-end: span 2;">
<div style="vertical-align:top; padding: 0 0 0 7px;"><p><span class="template_sbc"><b>Overcharged:</b></span> <b>Zeri</b> gains <span class="basic-tooltip" style="border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;" title="Can exceed Zeri&#39;s attack speed cap"><span class="ll-item navbox">Champions hit with Martial Cadence (P)</span><span><span style="color: #F5EE99; white-space:normal"><span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Attack_speed" title="Attack speed"><img alt="Attack speed icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="15" height="15" data-image-name="Attack speed icon.png" data-image-key="Attack_speed_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/9/91/Attack_speed_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/15?cb=20170515203443" class="lazyload" /></a>&#160;30% <b>bonus</b> attack speed</span></span></span></span> and <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions killed 5s before or after using Chronobreak (R)</span><span><span style="color: #FFFDC9; white-space:normal"><span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Movement_speed" title="Movement speed"><img alt="Movement speed icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="15" height="15" data-image-name="Movement speed icon.png" data-image-key="Movement_speed_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/e/ea/Movement_speed_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/15?cb=20170515203540" class="lazyload" /></a>&#160;10% <b>bonus</b> movement speed</span></span></span>. <i><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Burst Fire 3" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire_3" title="Burst Fire"><img alt="Burst Fire" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Burst Fire 3.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Burst_Fire_3.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/de/Zeri_Burst_Fire_3.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20220108011914" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire_3" title="Zeri/LoL">Burst Fire</a></span></span></i> is empowered to have a 20% shorter cast time and instead fire 3 rounds that travel with increased speed and chain to the nearest <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Sight"><a href="/wiki/Sight" title="Sight"><img alt="Sight icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Sight icon.png" data-image-key="Sight_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/0e/Sight_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20130928145820" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Sight" title="Sight">visible</a></span> enemy within 650 units of the target, up to 4 subsequent targets, to deal <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions stunned with Pyromania (P)</span><span><span style="color:orange; white-space:normal">25% AD</span></span> <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions killed from outside standard Attack range</span><span><span style="color: #FF8C34; white-space:normal">physical damage</span></span>. This damage can <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Critically strike"><a href="/wiki/Critical_strike" title="Critical strike"><img alt="Critical strike icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Critical strike icon.png" data-image-key="Critical_strike_icon.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/41/Critical_strike_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20191126102550" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Critical_strike" title="Critical strike">critically strike</a></span> for <span class="ll-item navbox">Lethal damage prevented with healing from Bountiful Harvest (W)</span><span><span style="color: #944B00; white-space:normal">(175%&#160;+&#160;<span class="inline-image label-after item-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-item="Infinity Edge" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Infinity_Edge" title="40%"><img alt="40%" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Infinity Edge item.png" data-image-key="Infinity_Edge_item.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/15/Infinity_Edge_item.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20201104234931" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Infinity_Edge" title="Infinity Edge">40%</a></span></span>)</span></span> <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions killed from outside standard Attack range</span><span><span style="color: #FF8C34; white-space:normal">physical damage</span></span>.</p></div>
</div><div style="text-align:center; padding:7px; vertical-align:top;">&#32;</div>
<div style="grid-column-end: span 2;">
<div style="vertical-align:top; padding: 0 0 0 7px;"><p>During <i>Overcharged</i>, <b>Zeri</b> can generate <a href="/wiki/Stack" title="Stack">stacks</a> of <i>Hypercharged</i> from enemy champions that last 1.<small>5</small> seconds. She generates 1 stack for each one she hits with an ability or <i><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Basic Attack 2" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Basic_Attack_2" title="charged"><img alt="charged" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Living Battery 2.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Living_Battery_2.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/55/Zeri_Living_Battery_2.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20220108011853" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Basic_Attack_2" title="Zeri/LoL">charged</a></span></span></i> basic attack, increased to 3 on abilities that <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Critically strike"><a href="/wiki/Critical_strike" title="Critical strike"><img alt="Critical strike icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Critical strike icon.png" data-image-key="Critical_strike_icon.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/41/Critical_strike_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20191126102550" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Critical_strike" title="Critical strike">critically strike</a></span>. Subsequent hits refresh the duration of <i>Hypercharged</i>. <i><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Burst Fire 3" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire_3" title="Burst Fire"><img alt="Burst Fire" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Burst Fire 3.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Burst_Fire_3.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/de/Zeri_Burst_Fire_3.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20220108011914" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire_3" title="Zeri/LoL">Burst Fire</a></span></span></i> grants stacks only against the first target hit.</p></div>
</div><div style="text-align:center; padding:7px; vertical-align:top;">&#32;</div>
<div style="grid-column-end: span 2;">
<div style="vertical-align:top; padding: 0 0 0 7px;"><p><span class="template_sbc"><b>Hypercharged:</b></span> For each stack, <b>Zeri</b> gains <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions killed 5s before or after using Chronobreak (R)</span><span><span style="color: #FFFDC9; white-space:normal"><span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Movement_speed" title="Movement speed"><img alt="Movement speed icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="15" height="15" data-image-name="Movement speed icon.png" data-image-key="Movement_speed_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/e/ea/Movement_speed_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/15?cb=20170515203540" class="lazyload" /></a>&#160;0.<small>5</small>% <b>bonus</b> movement speed</span></span></span>.</p></div>
</div>
<div style="vertical-align:top; padding: 5.2px 7px 0 10em; font-style:italic; font-size:larger; grid-column-end: span 3;"><span><audio hidden="" class="ext-audiobutton" data-volume="0.7" preload="none"><source src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/17/Zeri_Original_R_0.ogg/revision/latest?cb=20220526192136" type="application/ogg" /><a href="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/17/Zeri_Original_R_0.ogg/revision/latest?cb=20220526192136">Link</a></audio><a class="ext-audiobutton" data-state="play" title="Play/Pause">▶️</a></span><sup><a href="/wiki/File:Zeri_Original_R_0.ogg" title="File:Zeri Original R 0.ogg">&#160;&#160;</a></sup> <i>"Lightning crash!"</i></div></div></div></div></div><div style="clear:both"></div>
