https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/54/Zeri_PrestigeFrightNightSkin.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20240911004604" class="image"><img alt="Zeri PrestigeFrightNightSkin" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1215" height="717" data-image-name="Zeri PrestigeFrightNightSkin.jpg" data-image-key="Zeri_PrestigeFrightNightSkin.jpg" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/54/Zeri_PrestigeFrightNightSkin.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20240911004604" class="lazyload" /></a></div><div style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0.6);border-radius:6px 6px 0 0;line-height:24px;bottom:0;height:24px;right:0;left:0;font-size:20px;justify-content:space-between;border-right:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.25);border-left:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.25);position:absolute;display:flex;border-top:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.25);z-index:100;align-items:flex-end;"><div style="color:#d3c7aa;flex:4 1 0px;text-align:center;font-weight:700;"><span title="29">Prestige Fright Night</span></div><div style="text-align:center;flex:1 1 0px;"><span class="plainlinks"><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" class="external text" href="https://www.modelviewer.lol/model-viewer?id=221029"><span class="button" title="View in 3D" style="text-align:center; border-radius: 2px;"><b>View in 3D</b></span></a></span></div><div class="skinviewer-price" style="flex 1 1 0px; text-align:center;" title="2000 Worlds 2024 Tokens">Special</div><div style="text-align:center;padding-right:2px;color:#c9aa71;flex:1 1 0px;font-size:smaller;">25.09.2024</div></div></div><div class="skinviewer-info" style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);padding:15px;font-family:BeaufortLoL;font-size:14px;"><div class="skinviewer-info-lore"><div style="line-height: 1.6em; text-align: center; font-size: 15px;">Striking fear into the hearts of the unfashionable with her bold asymmetrical hair and oversized coat crawling with fine spider silk, Zeri's shocking new look is just to die for.</div><div><div class="center"><div class="floatnone"><img alt="Separator" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="400" height="7" data-image-name="Separator.png" data-image-key="Separator.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/10/Separator.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/400?cb=20180110165522" class="lazyload" /></div></div></div></div><div class="skinviewer-info-kleine-bilder" style="display:flex;justify-content:center;"><div style="padding-right:1em; text-align:center;"><img alt="Actor" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Actor.png" data-image-key="Actor.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/a/a9/Actor.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20180529054842" class="lazyload" />Vanille Velasquez</div><div style="padding-right:1em; text-align:center;"><img alt="Artist" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Artist.png" data-image-key="Artist.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/a/a5/Artist.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20180528201217" class="lazyload" />Herbie Wang, Kudos&#160;Productions</div><div style="padding-right:1em; text-align:center;"><img alt="Set piece" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Set piece.png" data-image-key="Set_piece.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/5d/Set_piece.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20180529081027" class="lazyload" /> <a href="/wiki/Neighborhood_Nightmare_(Universe)" title="Neighborhood Nightmare (Universe)">Fright Night</a></div><div style="padding-right:1em; text-align:center;"><img alt="Loot ineligible" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Loot ineligible.png" data-image-key="Loot_ineligible.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/a/ab/Loot_ineligible.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20190905171326" class="lazyload" /> Loot ineligible</div></div><div class="skinviewer-info-grosse-bilder" style="display:flex;justify-content:center;padding-top:5px;"><div style="padding:0 1em; text-align:center;"><div class="skin-viewer-text-icon"><img alt="New effects" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="50" height="50" data-image-name="New effects.png" data-image-key="New_effects.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/54/New_effects.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/50?cb=20180330200341" class="lazyload" /></div><div class="skin-viewer-text-icon">New SFX/VFX</div></div><div style="padding:0 1em; text-align:center;"><div class="skin-viewer-text-icon"><img alt="New animations" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="50" height="50" data-image-name="New animations.png" data-image-key="New_animations.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/55/New_animations.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/50?cb=20180330200340" class="lazyload" /></div><div class="skin-viewer-text-icon">New Animations/Recall</div></div></div><div class="skinviewer-info-variantof" style="text-align:center;"><div>This skin is a variant of  <span class="inline-image label-after skin-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-skin="Fright Night" data-champion="Zeri" data-game="lol"><span style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><img alt="Fright Night" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" title="Fright Night" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Zeri FrightNightCircle.png" data-image-key="Zeri_FrightNightCircle.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/9/9f/Zeri_FrightNightCircle.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240911005512" class="lazyload" /></span> <span style="white-space:normal;">Fright Night</span></span>. Store variants are discounted for multiple purchases.</div></div></div><div class="skinviewer-tab-chroma"></div></div></div></div>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Patch_history">Patch history</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a title="Sign in to edit" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" data-tracking-label="log-in-edit-section" data-action="edit-section" href="https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fleagueoflegends.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FZeri%2FLoL%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D3&amp;uselang=en" data-testid="log-in-edit-section"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-pencil-tiny"></use></svg></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<dl><dd><i>For the expanded patch notes, see <a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL/Patch_history" title="Zeri/LoL/Patch history">here</a>.</i></dd></dl>
<div style="overflow:auto; max-height:330px; width:100%; margin:3px 0; border:1px solid #AAAAAA; padding:0 0.5em 0 0.5em; box-sizing:border-box; -moz-box-sizing:border-box; -moz-border-radius-topleft:0.5em; background:transparent; border-radius:4px;">
<dl><dt><a href="/wiki/V14.18" title="V14.18">V14.18</a></dt></dl>
<ul><li><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Living Battery" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Living_Battery" title="Living Battery"><img alt="Living Battery" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Living Battery.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Living_Battery.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/dd/Zeri_Living_Battery.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20220108011846" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Living_Battery" title="Zeri/LoL">Living Battery</a></span></span>
<ul><li>Charged attack base damage changed <span class="pp-tooltip" style="position:relative; border-bottom:1px dotted; cursor:help;" data-start="75;" data-finish="160;" data-bot_values="75;80;85;90;95;100;105;110;115;120;125;130;135;140;145;150;155;160" data-top_values="">75 &#8722; 160 (based on level)</span> from <span class="pp-tooltip" style="position:relative; border-bottom:1px dotted; cursor:help;" data-useformula="90+(110/17)*(x-1)*(0.7025+0.0175*(x-1))" data-bot_values="90;94.66;99.54;104.66;109.99;115.56;121.35;127.37;133.61;140.08;146.78;153.7;160.85;168.23;175.83;183.66;191.72;200" data-top_values="">90 &#8722; 200 (based on level)</span>. <i>Formula changed.</i></li>
<li>Charged attack health ratio changed to <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions killed with Comeuppance (R)</span><span><span style="color: #1F995C; white-space:normal"><span class="pp-tooltip" style="position:relative; border-bottom:1px dotted; cursor:help;" data-start="1;" data-finish="11;" data-bot_values="1;1.59;2.18;2.76;3.35;3.94;4.53;5.12;5.71;6.29;6.88;7.47;8.06;8.65;9.24;9.82;10.41;11" data-top_values="" data-bot_key="%">1% &#8722; 11% (based on level)</span> of target's <b>maximum</b> health</span></span> from <span class="ll-item navbox">Damage mitigated by Master-At-Arms (R)</span><span><span style="color: #1F995C; white-space:normal"><span class="pp-tooltip" style="position:relative; border-bottom:1px dotted; cursor:help;" data-useformula="1+(14/17)*(x-1)*(0.7025+0.0175*(x-1))" data-bot_values="1;1.59;2.21;2.87;3.54;4.25;4.99;5.76;6.55;7.37;8.23;9.11;10.02;10.96;11.92;12.92;13.95;15" data-top_values="" data-bot_key="%">1% &#8722; 15% (based on level)</span></span></span>. <i>Formula changed.</i></li></ul></li></ul>
<dl><dt><a href="/wiki/V14.8" title="V14.8">V14.8</a></dt></dl>
<ul><li>Stats
<ul><li>Base health reduced to 600 from 630.</li></ul></li></ul>
<dl><dt><a href="/wiki/V14.3" title="V14.3">V14.3</a></dt></dl>
<ul><li>Stats
<ul><li>Base attack damage increased to 56 from 53.</li></ul></li>
<li><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Lightning Crash" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Lightning_Crash" title="Lightning Crash"><img alt="Lightning Crash" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Lightning Crash.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Lightning_Crash.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/2/23/Zeri_Lightning_Crash.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813185746" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Lightning_Crash" title="Zeri/LoL">Lightning Crash</a></span></span>
<ul><li>Cooldown reduced to 80 / 75 / 70 seconds from 100 / 85 / 70.</li></ul></li></ul>
<dl><dt><a href="/wiki/V13.24" title="V13.24">V13.24</a></dt></dl>
<ul><li>Stats
<ul><li>Attack damage growth increased to 2 from 1.<small>3</small>.</li></ul></li>
<li><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Ultrashock Laser" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Ultrashock_Laser" title="Ultrashock Laser"><img alt="Ultrashock Laser" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Ultrashock Laser.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Ultrashock_Laser.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/45/Zeri_Ultrashock_Laser.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813185815" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Ultrashock_Laser" title="Zeri/LoL">Ultrashock Laser</a></span></span>
<ul><li>Base damage increased to 30 / 70 / 110 / 150 / 190 from 20 / 60 / 100 / 140 / 180.</li></ul></li></ul>
<dl><dt><a href="/wiki/V13.19" title="V13.19">V13.19</a></dt></dl>
<ul><li>Stats
<ul><li>Base movement speed reduced to 330 from 335.</li></ul></li></ul>
<dl><dt><a href="/wiki/V13.14" title="V13.14">V13.14</a></dt></dl>
<ul><li><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Burst Fire" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire" title="Burst Fire"><img alt="Burst Fire" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Burst Fire.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Burst_Fire.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/1e/Zeri_Burst_Fire.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813185727" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire" title="Zeri/LoL">Burst Fire</a></span></span>
<ul><li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Bug Fix:</b></span> Now deals the correct amount of damage against <span class="champion-ability-icon"><span class="inline-image label-after champion-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Shaco" data-skin="Original" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Shaco/LoL" title="Shaco&#39;s"><img alt="Shaco&#39;s" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Shaco OriginalSquare.png" data-image-key="Shaco_OriginalSquare.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/e/e1/Shaco_OriginalSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20230821213937" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Shaco/LoL" title="Shaco/LoL">Shaco's</a></span></span> <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Shaco" data-ability="Jack in the Box" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Shaco/LoL#Jack_in_the_Box" title="Jack in the Box"><img alt="Jack in the Box" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Shaco Jack in the Box.png" data-image-key="Shaco_Jack_in_the_Box.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/73/Shaco_Jack_in_the_Box.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813160824" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Shaco/LoL#Jack_in_the_Box" title="Shaco/LoL">Jack in the Box</a></span></span></span>.</li></ul></li></ul>
<dl><dt><a href="/wiki/V13.12" title="V13.12">V13.12</a></dt></dl>
<ul><li>Stats
<ul><li>Base movement speed increased to 335 from 330.</li></ul></li>
<li><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Living Battery" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Living_Battery" title="Living Battery"><img alt="Living Battery" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Living Battery.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Living_Battery.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/dd/Zeri_Living_Battery.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20220108011846" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Living_Battery" title="Zeri/LoL">Living Battery</a></span></span>
<ul><li>Tooltip now contains information about <b>Zeri's</b> basic attacks.</li>
<li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Removed Innate:</b></span> <b>Zeri</b> absorbs the energy of <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Shield"><a href="/wiki/Shield" title="Shield"><img alt="Hybrid resistances icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Hybrid resistances icon.png" data-image-key="Hybrid_resistances_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/55/Hybrid_resistances_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20170516021237" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Shield" title="Shield">shields</a></span> she damages, granting herself a shield equal to 45% of the <span class="basic-tooltip" style="border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;" title="Damage calculated after modifiers">post-mitigation damage</span> dealt to the shield. Each instance of shield gained by <i>Living Battery</i> lasts for 3 seconds.</li>
<li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Removed Innate - Gotta Zip!:</b></span> Whenever <b>Zeri</b> gains a shield, she gains <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Attack_speed" title="Attack speed"><img alt="Attack speed icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="15" height="15" data-image-name="Attack speed icon.png" data-image-key="Attack_speed_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/9/91/Attack_speed_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/15?cb=20170515203443" class="lazyload" /></a>&#160;<span class="ll-item navbox">Champions killed 5s before or after using Chronobreak (R)</span><span><span style="color: #FFFDC9; white-space:normal">10% <b>bonus</b> movement speed</span></span></span> for 2 seconds.</li></ul></li>
<li><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Burst Fire" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire" title="Burst Fire"><img alt="Burst Fire" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Burst Fire.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Burst_Fire.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/1e/Zeri_Burst_Fire.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813185727" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire" title="Zeri/LoL">Burst Fire</a></span></span>
<ul><li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Removed:</b></span> No longer triggers <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Spellblade"><a href="/wiki/Named_item_effect#Spellblade" title="Named item effect"><img alt="Sheen item" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Sheen item.png" data-image-key="Sheen_item.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/c/c6/Sheen_item.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20201118210052" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Named_item_effect#Spellblade" title="Named item effect">Spellblade</a></span>.</li></ul></li>
