<ul><li><span class="template_sbc"><b>New:</b></span>
<ul><li><b>Zeri</b> discharges a nova of electricity around her that deals 175 / 275 / 375 <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions stunned with Pyromania (P)</span><span><span style="color:orange; white-space:normal">(+ 100% <b>bonus</b> AD)</span></span> <span class="ll-item navbox">Multiple champions hit with Between Worlds (R)</span><span><span style="color: #7A6DFF; white-space:normal">(+ 110% AP)</span></span> <span class="ll-item navbox">Damage mitigated with Shifting Sands (E)</span><span><span style="color: #00B0F0; white-space:normal">magic damage</span></span> to nearby enemies.</li>
<li>If <i>Lightning Crash</i> hits at least one enemy champion, <b>Zeri</b> becomes <i>Overcharged</i> for 5 seconds. Damaging an enemy increases the duration by 1.<small>5</small> seconds, up to its original duration.</li>
<li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Overcharge:</b></span> <b>Zeri</b> gains <span class="basic-tooltip" style="border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;" title="Can exceed Zeri&#39;s attack speed cap"><span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Attack_damage" title="Attack damage"><img alt="Attack damage icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="15" height="15" data-image-name="Attack damage icon.png" data-image-key="Attack_damage_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/75/Attack_damage_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/15?cb=20170515203443" class="lazyload" /></a>&#160;<span class="ll-item navbox">Champions hit with Martial Cadence (P)</span><span><span style="color: #F5EE99; white-space:normal">30% <b>bonus</b> attack speed</span></span></span></span> and <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Attack_speed" title="Attack speed"><img alt="Attack speed icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="15" height="15" data-image-name="Attack speed icon.png" data-image-key="Attack_speed_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/9/91/Attack_speed_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/15?cb=20170515203443" class="lazyload" /></a>&#160;<span class="ll-item navbox">Champions killed 5s before or after using Chronobreak (R)</span><span><span style="color: #FFFDC9; white-space:normal">10% <b>bonus</b> movement speed</span></span></span>. <i><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Burst Fire 3" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire_3" title="Burst Fire"><img alt="Burst Fire" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Burst Fire 3.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Burst_Fire_3.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/de/Zeri_Burst_Fire_3.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20220108011914" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire_3" title="Zeri/LoL">Burst Fire</a></span></span></i> is empowered to have a 20% shorter cast time and instead fire 3 rounds that travel with increased speed. These attacks chain to the nearest <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Sight"><a href="/wiki/Sight" title="Sight"><img alt="Sight icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Sight icon.png" data-image-key="Sight_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/0e/Sight_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20130928145820" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Sight" title="Sight">visible</a></span> enemy within 650-units of the target, up to 4 subsequent targets, dealing <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions stunned with Pyromania (P)</span><span><span style="color:orange; white-space:normal">25% AD</span></span> <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions killed from outside standard Attack range</span><span><span style="color: #FF8C34; white-space:normal">physical damage</span></span>, which can <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Critical strike"><a href="/wiki/Critical_strike" title="Critical strike"><img alt="Critical strike icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Critical strike icon.png" data-image-key="Critical_strike_icon.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/41/Critical_strike_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20191126102550" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Critical_strike" title="Critical strike">critically strike</a></span> for <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions stunned with Pyromania (P)</span><span><span style="color:orange; white-space:normal">(18.<small>75</small>%&#160;+&#160;<span class="inline-image label-after item-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-item="Infinity Edge" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Infinity_Edge" title="8.75%"><img alt="8" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Infinity Edge item.png" data-image-key="Infinity_Edge_item.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/15/Infinity_Edge_item.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20201104234931" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Infinity_Edge" title="Infinity Edge">8.<small>75</small>%</a></span></span>) AD</span></span> <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions killed from outside standard Attack range</span><span><span style="color: #FF8C34; white-space:normal"><b>bonus</b> physical damage</span></span>.</li>
<li>Additionally, <b>Zeri</b> generates stacks from hitting enemy champions, gaining <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions killed 5s before or after using Chronobreak (R)</span><span><span style="color: #FFFDC9; white-space:normal">0.<small>5</small>% <b>bonus</b> movement speed</span></span> per stack for 1.<small>5</small> seconds. She generates 1 stack for each one she hits with a <i><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Basic Attack 2" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Basic_Attack_2" title="charged"><img alt="charged" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Living Battery 2.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Living_Battery_2.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/55/Zeri_Living_Battery_2.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20220108011853" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Basic_Attack_2" title="Zeri/LoL">charged</a></span></span></i> basic attack or ability, increased to 3 on abilities that <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Critically strike"><a href="/wiki/Critical_strike" title="Critical strike"><img alt="Critical strike icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Critical strike icon.png" data-image-key="Critical_strike_icon.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/41/Critical_strike_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20191126102550" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Critical_strike" title="Critical strike">critically strike</a></span>. <i><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Burst Fire 3" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire_3" title="Burst Fire"><img alt="Burst Fire" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Burst Fire 3.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Burst_Fire_3.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/de/Zeri_Burst_Fire_3.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20220108011914" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire_3" title="Zeri/LoL">Burst Fire</a></span></span></i> grants stacks only against the first target hit.</li></ul></li>
<li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Old:</b></span>
<ul><li><b>Zeri</b> discharges a nova of electricity around her that deals 150 / 250 / 350 <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions stunned with Pyromania (P)</span><span><span style="color:orange; white-space:normal">(+ 80% <b>bonus</b> AD)</span></span> <span class="ll-item navbox">Multiple champions hit with Between Worlds (R)</span><span><span style="color: #7A6DFF; white-space:normal">(+ 80% AP)</span></span> <span class="ll-item navbox">Damage mitigated with Shifting Sands (E)</span><span><span style="color: #00B0F0; white-space:normal">magic damage</span></span> to nearby enemies.</li>
<li>If <i>Lightning Crash</i> hits at least one enemy champion, <b>Zeri</b> becomes <i>Overcharged</i> for 6 seconds.</li>
<li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Overcharge:</b></span> <b>Zeri</b> gains <span class="basic-tooltip" style="border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;" title="Can exceed Zeri&#39;s attack speed cap"><span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Attack_damage" title="Attack damage"><img alt="Attack damage icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="15" height="15" data-image-name="Attack damage icon.png" data-image-key="Attack_damage_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/75/Attack_damage_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/15?cb=20170515203443" class="lazyload" /></a>&#160;<span class="ll-item navbox">Champions hit with Martial Cadence (P)</span><span><span style="color: #F5EE99; white-space:normal">30% <b>bonus</b> attack speed</span></span></span></span>. <i><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Burst Fire 3" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire_3" title="Burst Fire"><img alt="Burst Fire" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Burst Fire 3.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Burst_Fire_3.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/de/Zeri_Burst_Fire_3.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20220108011914" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire_3" title="Zeri/LoL">Burst Fire</a></span></span></i> is empowered to have a 20% shorter cast time and instead fire 3 rounds that travel with increased speed and deal 5 / 10 / 15 <span class="ll-item navbox">Multiple champions hit with Between Worlds (R)</span><span><span style="color: #7A6DFF; white-space:normal">(+ 15% AP)</span></span> <span class="ll-item navbox">Damage mitigated with Shifting Sands (E)</span><span><span style="color: #00B0F0; white-space:normal"><b>bonus</b> magic damage</span></span> to the first enemy hit and the nearest <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Sight"><a href="/wiki/Sight" title="Sight"><img alt="Sight icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Sight icon.png" data-image-key="Sight_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/0e/Sight_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20130928145820" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Sight" title="Sight">visible</a></span> enemy within 450-units of the target, chaining up to 4 subsequent targets. Secondary targets are dealt <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions stunned with Pyromania (P)</span><span><span style="color:orange; white-space:normal">25% AD</span></span> <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions killed from outside standard Attack range</span><span><span style="color: #FF8C34; white-space:normal">physical damage</span></span>, which can <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Critical strike"><a href="/wiki/Critical_strike" title="Critical strike"><img alt="Critical strike icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Critical strike icon.png" data-image-key="Critical_strike_icon.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/41/Critical_strike_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20191126102550" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Critical_strike" title="Critical strike">critically strike</a></span> for <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions stunned with Pyromania (P)</span><span><span style="color:orange; white-space:normal">(18.<small>75</small>%&#160;+&#160;<span class="inline-image label-after item-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-item="Infinity Edge" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Infinity_Edge" title="8.75%"><img alt="8" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Infinity Edge item.png" data-image-key="Infinity_Edge_item.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/15/Infinity_Edge_item.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20201104234931" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Infinity_Edge" title="Infinity Edge">8.<small>75</small>%</a></span></span>) AD</span></span> <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions killed from outside standard Attack range</span><span><span style="color: #FF8C34; white-space:normal"><b>bonus</b> physical damage</span></span>. The <span class="ll-item navbox">Damage mitigated with Shifting Sands (E)</span><span><span style="color: #00B0F0; white-space:normal"><b>bonus</b> magic damage</span></span> is affected by <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Critical strike"><a href="/wiki/Critical_strike" title="Critical strike"><img alt="Critical strike icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Critical strike icon.png" data-image-key="Critical_strike_icon.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/41/Critical_strike_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20191126102550" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Critical_strike" title="Critical strike">critical strike</a></span> modifiers.</li>
<li>Additionally, <b>Zeri</b> generates stacks of <i>Overcharge</i> from hitting enemy champions, gaining <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions killed 5s before or after using Chronobreak (R)</span><span><span style="color: #FFFDC9; white-space:normal">0.<small>5</small>% <b>bonus</b> movement speed</span></span> per stack. She generates 1 stack for each one she hits with a <i><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Basic Attack 2" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Basic_Attack_2" title="charged"><img alt="charged" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Living Battery 2.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Living_Battery_2.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/55/Zeri_Living_Battery_2.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20220108011853" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Basic_Attack_2" title="Zeri/LoL">charged</a></span></span></i> basic attack or ability, increased to 3 on abilities that <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Critically strike"><a href="/wiki/Critical_strike" title="Critical strike"><img alt="Critical strike icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Critical strike icon.png" data-image-key="Critical_strike_icon.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/41/Critical_strike_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20191126102550" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Critical_strike" title="Critical strike">critically strike</a></span> and 8 on <i>Lightning Crash</i>. <i><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Burst Fire 3" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire_3" title="Burst Fire"><img alt="Burst Fire" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Burst Fire 3.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Burst_Fire_3.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/de/Zeri_Burst_Fire_3.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20220108011914" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire_3" title="Zeri/LoL">Burst Fire</a></span></span></i> grants stacks only against the first target hit. <i>Overcharge's</i> duration is extended by 2 seconds whenever <b>Zeri</b> generates a stack, up to its original duration.</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul>
