<ul><li>Damage at 600% was equivalent to <span class="pp-tooltip" style="position:relative; border-bottom:1px dotted; cursor:help;" data-useformula="6*10+(6*15/17)*(x-1)*(0.7025+0.0175*(x-1))" data-bot_values="60;63.81;67.81;71.99;76.36;80.91;85.65;90.57;95.68;100.98;106.46;112.12;117.97;124.01;130.23;136.63;143.22;150" data-top_values="">60 &#8722; 150 (based on level)</span> <span class="ll-item navbox">Multiple champions hit with Between Worlds (R)</span><span><span style="color: #7A6DFF; white-space:normal">(+ 18% AP)</span></span>.</li></ul></li>
<li><span class="template_sbc"><b>New Effect:</b></span> Uncharged basic attacks now execute targets below <span class="pp-tooltip" style="position:relative; border-bottom:1px dotted; cursor:help;" data-start="60;" data-finish="150;" data-bot_values="60;65.29;70.59;75.88;81.18;86.47;91.76;97.06;102.35;107.65;112.94;118.24;123.53;128.82;134.12;139.41;144.71;150" data-top_values="">60 &#8722; 150 (based on level)</span> <span class="ll-item navbox">Multiple champions hit with Between Worlds (R)</span><span><span style="color: #7A6DFF; white-space:normal">(+ 18% AP)</span></span> health.
<ul><li>Does not execute if the target is shielded or invulnerable.</li></ul></li></ul></li>
