<ul><li>Uncharged base damage reduced to <span class="pp-tooltip" style="position:relative; border-bottom:1px dotted; cursor:help;" data-useformula="10+((25-10)/17)*(x-1)*(0.7025+0.0175*(x-1))" data-bot_values="10;10.64;11.3;12;12.73;13.49;14.28;15.1;15.95;16.83;17.74;18.69;19.66;20.67;21.7;22.77;23.87;25" data-top_values="">10 &#8722; 25 (based on level)</span> from <span class="pp-tooltip" style="position:relative; border-bottom:1px dotted; cursor:help;" data-useformula="15+((40-15)/17)*(x-1)*(0.7025+0.0175*(x-1))" data-bot_values="15;16.06;17.17;18.33;19.54;20.81;22.13;23.49;24.91;26.38;27.9;29.48;31.1;32.78;34.51;36.29;38.12;40" data-top_values="">15 &#8722; 40 (based on level)</span>.</li>
