<li>Uncharged bonus damage factor against low health targets increased to 500% from 300%.
<ul><li>Uncharged base damage against low health targets reduced to <span class="pp-tooltip" style="position:relative; border-bottom:1px dotted; cursor:help;" data-useformula="60+((150-60)/17)*(x-1)*(0.7025+0.0175*(x-1))" data-bot_values="60;63.81;67.81;71.99;76.36;80.91;85.65;90.57;95.68;100.98;106.46;112.12;117.97;124.01;130.23;136.63;143.22;150" data-top_values="">60 &#8722; 150 (based on level)</span> from <span class="pp-tooltip" style="position:relative; border-bottom:1px dotted; cursor:help;" data-useformula="60+((160-60)/17)*(x-1)*(0.7025+0.0175*(x-1))" data-bot_values="60;64.24;68.68;73.32;78.18;83.24;88.5;93.97;99.65;105.53;111.62;117.91;124.41;131.12;138.03;145.15;152.47;160" data-top_values="">60 &#8722; 160 (based on level)</span>.</li>
<li>Uncharged AP ratio against low health targets increased to <span class="ll-item navbox">Multiple champions hit with Between Worlds (R)</span><span><span style="color: #7A6DFF; white-space:normal">18% AP</span></span> from <span class="ll-item navbox">Multiple champions hit with Between Worlds (R)</span><span><span style="color: #7A6DFF; white-space:normal">16% AP</span></span>.</li></ul></li>
