<dl><dt><a href="/wiki/V12.3" title="V12.3">V12.3</a></dt></dl>
<ul><li>General
<ul><li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Bug Fix:</b></span> Several VFX now properly display correctly upon reconnecting to a game.</li></ul></li>
<li>Stats
<ul><li>Base movement speed reduced to 325 from 330.</li></ul></li>
<li><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Basic Attack" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Basic_Attack" title="Basic Attack"><img alt="Basic Attack" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Basic Attack.png" data-image-key="Basic_Attack.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/c/cd/Basic_Attack.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20200517010633" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Basic_Attack" title="Zeri/LoL">Basic Attack</a></span></span>
<ul><li>Health ratio reduced to <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions killed with Comeuppance (R)</span><span><span style="color: #1F995C; white-space:normal"><span class="pp-tooltip" style="position:relative; border-bottom:1px dotted; cursor:help;" data-useformula="3+(17/17)*(x-1)*(0.7025+0.0002*(x-1))" data-bot_values="3;3.7;4.41;5.11;5.81;6.52;7.22;7.93;8.63;9.34;10.05;10.75;11.46;12.17;12.87;13.58;14.29;15" data-top_values="" data-bot_key="%">3% &#8722; 15% (based on level)</span> of target's <b>maximum</b> health</span></span> from <span class="ll-item navbox">Damage mitigated by Master-At-Arms (R)</span><span><span style="color: #1F995C; white-space:normal"><span class="pp-tooltip" style="position:relative; border-bottom:1px dotted; cursor:help;" data-useformula="3+(17/17)*(x-1)*(0.7025+0.0175*(x-1))" data-bot_values="3;3.72;4.47;5.27;6.09;6.95;7.85;8.78;9.74;10.74;11.78;12.85;13.95;15.09;16.27;17.48;18.72;20" data-top_values="" data-bot_key="%">3% &#8722; 20% (based on level)</span></span></span></li></ul></li>
<li><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Burst Fire" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire" title="Burst Fire"><img alt="Burst Fire" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Burst Fire.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Burst_Fire.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/1e/Zeri_Burst_Fire.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813185727" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire" title="Zeri/LoL">Burst Fire</a></span></span>
<ul><li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Bug Fix:</b></span> <span class="inline-image label-after item-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-item="Runaan&#39;s Hurricane" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Runaan%27s_Hurricane" title="Runaan&#39;s Hurricane"><img alt="Runaan&#39;s Hurricane" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Runaan&#39;s Hurricane item.png" data-image-key="Runaan%27s_Hurricane_item.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/f/f5/Runaan%27s_Hurricane_item.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20201027214148" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Runaan%27s_Hurricane" title="Runaan&#39;s Hurricane">Runaan's Hurricane</a></span></span> Winds Fury now triggers even if she is facing away from the target when the rounds hit.</li></ul></li>
<li><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Spark Surge" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Spark_Surge" title="Spark Surge"><img alt="Spark Surge" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Spark Surge.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Spark_Surge.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/b/b7/Zeri_Spark_Surge.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813185756" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Spark_Surge" title="Zeri/LoL">Spark Surge</a></span></span>
<ul><li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Bug Fix:</b></span> Now properly vaults over <span class="champion-ability-icon"><span class="inline-image label-after champion-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Anivia" data-skin="Original" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Anivia/LoL" title="Anivia&#39;s"><img alt="Anivia&#39;s" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Anivia OriginalSquare.png" data-image-key="Anivia_OriginalSquare.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/0e/Anivia_OriginalSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20151218185051" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Anivia/LoL" title="Anivia/LoL">Anivia's</a></span></span> <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Anivia" data-ability="Crystallize" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Anivia/LoL#Crystallize" title="Crystallize"><img alt="Crystallize" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Anivia Crystallize.png" data-image-key="Anivia_Crystallize.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/f/fd/Anivia_Crystallize.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240810171331" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Anivia/LoL#Crystallize" title="Anivia/LoL">Crystallize</a></span></span></span> and <span class="champion-ability-icon"><span class="inline-image label-after champion-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Trundle" data-skin="Original" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Trundle/LoL" title="Trundle&#39;s"><img alt="Trundle&#39;s" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Trundle OriginalSquare.png" data-image-key="Trundle_OriginalSquare.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/40/Trundle_OriginalSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20150402221506" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Trundle/LoL" title="Trundle/LoL">Trundle's</a></span></span> <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Trundle" data-ability="Pillar of Ice" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Trundle/LoL#Pillar_of_Ice" title="Pillar of Ice"><img alt="Pillar of Ice" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Trundle Pillar of Ice.png" data-image-key="Trundle_Pillar_of_Ice.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/8/8a/Trundle_Pillar_of_Ice.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813172049" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Trundle/LoL#Pillar_of_Ice" title="Trundle/LoL">Pillar of Ice</a></span></span></span> instead of dashing over them.</li></ul></li>
<li><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Lightning Crash" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Lightning_Crash" title="Lightning Crash"><img alt="Lightning Crash" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Lightning Crash.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Lightning_Crash.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/2/23/Zeri_Lightning_Crash.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813185746" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Lightning_Crash" title="Zeri/LoL">Lightning Crash</a></span></span>
<ul><li>Chain lightning base damage reduced to 10 / 15 / 20 from 10 / 20 / 30.</li>
<li><span class="template_sbc"><b>New Effect:</b></span> Chain lightning magic damage can now critically strike.</li></ul></li></ul>
<dl><dt><a href="/wiki/V12.2#January_26th_Hotfix" title="V12.2">V12.2</a> - January 26th Hotfix</dt></dl>
<ul><li><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Lightning Crash" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Lightning_Crash" title="Lightning Crash"><img alt="Lightning Crash" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Lightning Crash.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Lightning_Crash.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/2/23/Zeri_Lightning_Crash.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813185746" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Lightning_Crash" title="Zeri/LoL">Lightning Crash</a></span></span>
<ul><li><span class="template_sbc"><b>New Effect:</b></span> Bonus magic damage now only applies once per attack, rather than as an on-hit effect.</li></ul></li></ul>
<dl><dt><a href="/wiki/V12.2" title="V12.2">V12.2</a> - Added</dt></dl>
<ul><li><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Basic Attack" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Basic_Attack" title="Basic Attack"><img alt="Basic Attack" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Basic Attack.png" data-image-key="Basic_Attack.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/c/cd/Basic_Attack.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20200517010633" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Basic_Attack" title="Zeri/LoL">Basic Attack</a></span></span>
<ul><li><b>Zeri</b> generates 1 charge for every 40 units she travels by any means and 10 charge every time she casts <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Burst Fire" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire" title="Burst Fire"><img alt="Burst Fire" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Burst Fire.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Burst_Fire.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/1e/Zeri_Burst_Fire.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813185727" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire" title="Zeri/LoL">Burst Fire</a></span></span>, up to a maximum of 100 charge. Her basic attacks consume charge to deal <b>modified</b> damage. <b>Zeri</b> gains maximum charge when the game starts and upon respawning.</li>
<li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Basic Attack:</b></span> <b>Zeri</b> zaps her target, becoming <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Projectile"><a href="/wiki/Projectile" title="Projectile"><img alt="Projectile" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Projectile.png" data-image-key="Projectile.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/6/6b/Projectile.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20150816082407" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Projectile" title="Projectile">non-projectile</a></span> and applying spell effects as <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Spell damage"><a href="/wiki/Damage" title="Damage"><img alt="Disintegrate" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Annie Disintegrate.png" data-image-key="Annie_Disintegrate.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/b/bf/Annie_Disintegrate.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240810171544" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Damage" title="Damage">spell damage</a></span>. <b>Zeri's</b> basic attacks <b>cannot</b> <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Critical strike"><a href="/wiki/Critical_strike" title="Critical strike"><img alt="Critical strike icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Critical strike icon.png" data-image-key="Critical_strike_icon.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/41/Critical_strike_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20191126102550" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Critical_strike" title="Critical strike">critically strike</a></span> nor trigger <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="On-hit"><a href="/wiki/Attack_effects#On_Hitting" title="Attack effects"><img alt="On-hit icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="On-hit icon.png" data-image-key="On-hit_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/75/On-hit_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20201114055106" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Attack_effects#On_Hitting" title="Attack effects">on-hit</a></span> and <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="On-attack"><a href="/wiki/Attack_effects#On_Attacking" title="Attack effects">on-attack</a></span> effects.</li>
<li>While not at full charge, <b>Zeri's</b> attacks consume 10 charge to deal <span class="ll-item navbox">Damage mitigated by Master-At-Arms (R)</span><span><span style="color: #00B0F0; white-space:normal"><span class="pp-tooltip" style="position:relative; border-bottom:1px dotted; cursor:help;" data-useformula="15+(25/17)*(x-1)*(0.7025+0.0175*(x-1))" data-bot_values="15;16.06;17.17;18.33;19.54;20.81;22.13;23.49;24.91;26.38;27.9;29.48;31.1;32.78;34.51;36.29;38.12;40" data-top_values="">15 &#8722; 40 (based on level)</span></span></span> <span class="ll-item navbox">Multiple champions hit with Between Worlds (R)</span><span><span style="color: #7A6DFF; white-space:normal">(+ 4% AP)</span></span> <span class="ll-item navbox">Damage mitigated with Shifting Sands (E)</span><span><span style="color: #00B0F0; white-space:normal">magic damage</span></span>. Against enemies <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions killed with Comeuppance (R)</span><span><span style="color: #1F995C; white-space:normal"><b>below</b> 35% health</span></span>, this is increased<span id="container" class="container" style="cursor:help;"><span class="flipText1 active">「&#160;by 300%.&#160;」</span><span class="flipText2">「&#160;to <span class="ll-item navbox">Damage mitigated by Master-At-Arms (R)</span><span><span style="color: #00B0F0; white-space:normal"><span class="pp-tooltip" style="position:relative; border-bottom:1px dotted; cursor:help;" data-useformula="4*15+(4*25/17)*(x-1)*(0.7025+0.0175*(x-1))" data-bot_values="60;64.24;68.68;73.32;78.18;83.24;88.5;93.97;99.65;105.53;111.62;117.91;124.41;131.12;138.03;145.15;152.47;160" data-top_values="">60 &#8722; 160 (based on level)</span></span></span> <span class="ll-item navbox">Multiple champions hit with Between Worlds (R)</span><span><span style="color: #7A6DFF; white-space:normal">(+ 16% AP)</span></span>.&#160;」</span></span>She may still use an uncharged attack even while below 10 charge.</li>
<li>At full charge, <b>Zeri's</b> next attack will consume all charge to deal <span class="ll-item navbox">Damage mitigated by Master-At-Arms (R)</span><span><span style="color: #00B0F0; white-space:normal"><span class="pp-tooltip" style="position:relative; border-bottom:1px dotted; cursor:help;" data-useformula="90+(110/17)*(x-1)*(0.7025+0.0175*(x-1))" data-bot_values="90;94.66;99.54;104.66;109.99;115.56;121.35;127.37;133.61;140.08;146.78;153.7;160.85;168.23;175.83;183.66;191.72;200" data-top_values="">90 &#8722; 200 (based on level)</span></span></span> <span class="ll-item navbox">Multiple champions hit with Between Worlds (R)</span><span><span style="color: #7A6DFF; white-space:normal">(+ 80% AP)</span></span> <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions killed with Comeuppance (R)</span><span><span style="color: #1F995C; white-space:normal">(+ <span class="pp-tooltip" style="position:relative; border-bottom:1px dotted; cursor:help;" data-useformula="3+(17/17)*(x-1)*(0.7025+0.0175*(x-1))" data-bot_values="3;3.72;4.47;5.27;6.09;6.95;7.85;8.78;9.74;10.74;11.78;12.85;13.95;15.09;16.27;17.48;18.72;20" data-top_values="" data-bot_key="%">3% &#8722; 20% (based on level)</span> of target's <b>maximum</b> health)</span></span> <span class="ll-item navbox">Damage mitigated with Shifting Sands (E)</span><span><span style="color: #00B0F0; white-space:normal">magic damage</span></span> and <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Slow"><a href="/wiki/Slow" title="Slow"><img alt="Slow icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Slow icon.png" data-image-key="Slow_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/78/Slow_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20171201224744" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Slow" class="mw-redirect" title="Slow">slow</a></span> the target by <span class="pp-tooltip" style="position:relative; border-bottom:1px dotted; cursor:help;" data-top_label="&#91;&#91;File:Zeri Burst Fire.png&#124;20px&#124;border&#93;&#93; Burst Fire&#39;s rank" data-start="20;1" data-finish="40;5" data-bot_values="20;25;30;35;40" data-top_values="1;2;3;4;5" data-bot_key="%">20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40% (based on <a href="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/1e/Zeri_Burst_Fire.png/revision/latest?cb=20240813185727" class="image"><img alt="Zeri Burst Fire" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Burst Fire.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Burst_Fire.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/1e/Zeri_Burst_Fire.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813185727" /></a> Burst Fire's rank)</span> for 1.<small>5</small> seconds. The damage based on the target's health ratio is capped at 300 against <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Monsters"><a href="/wiki/Monster" title="Monster"><img alt="Monster icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Monster icon.png" data-image-key="Monster_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/d1/Monster_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20231028083627" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Monster" title="Monster">monsters</a></span>.</li>
<li><b>Zeri's</b> basic attacks have 500 attack range and are non-projectiles.</li></ul></li>
<li><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Living Battery" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Living_Battery" title="Living Battery"><img alt="Living Battery" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Living Battery old.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Living_Battery_old.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/7d/Zeri_Living_Battery_old.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20220107163532" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Living_Battery" title="Zeri/LoL">Living Battery</a></span></span> (Innate)
<ul><li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Innate:</b></span> <b>Zeri</b> absorbs the energy of <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Shield"><a href="/wiki/Shield" title="Shield"><img alt="Hybrid resistances icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Hybrid resistances icon.png" data-image-key="Hybrid_resistances_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/55/Hybrid_resistances_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20170516021237" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Shield" title="Shield">shields</a></span> she damages, shielding herself equal to 60% of the <span class="basic-tooltip" style="border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;" title="Damage calculated after modifiers">post-mitigation damage</span> dealt to the shield. Each instance of shield gained by <i>Living Battery</i> lasts for 3 seconds.</li>
<li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Innate:</b></span> Whenever <b>Zeri</b> receives a <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Shield"><a href="/wiki/Shield" title="Shield"><img alt="Hybrid resistances icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Hybrid resistances icon.png" data-image-key="Hybrid_resistances_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/55/Hybrid_resistances_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20170516021237" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Shield" title="Shield">shield</a></span>, she gains <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions killed 5s before or after using Chronobreak (R)</span><span><span style="color: #FFFDC9; white-space:normal">10% <b>bonus</b> movement speed</span></span> for 3 seconds.</li></ul></li>
<li><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Burst Fire" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire" title="Burst Fire"><img alt="Burst Fire" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Burst Fire.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Burst_Fire.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/1e/Zeri_Burst_Fire.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813185727" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire" title="Zeri/LoL">Burst Fire</a></span></span> (Q)
<ul><li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Passive:</b></span> <b>Zeri's</b> <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Slow"><a href="/wiki/Slow" title="Slow"><img alt="Slow icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Slow icon.png" data-image-key="Slow_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/78/Slow_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20171201224744" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Slow" class="mw-redirect" title="Slow">slow</a></span> application from a <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Basic Attack 2" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Basic_Attack_2" title="charged"><img alt="charged" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Living Battery 2.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Living_Battery_2.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/55/Zeri_Living_Battery_2.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20220108011853" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Basic_Attack_2" title="Zeri/LoL">charged</a></span></span> basic attack has its strength increased to 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40%.</li>
<li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Active:</b></span> <b>Zeri</b> fires a burst of 7 rounds in the target direction that deal a total of 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 / 30 <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions stunned with Pyromania (P)</span><span><span style="color:orange; white-space:normal">(+ 110% AD)</span></span> <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions killed from outside standard Attack range</span><span><span style="color: #FF8C34; white-space:normal">physical damage</span></span> to the first enemy hit.</li>
<li><i>Burst Fire's</i> effects are treated as a basic attack; it can hit any enemy unit a typical basic attack can, deals <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Basic damage"><a href="/wiki/Damage" title="Damage"><img alt="Basic Attack" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Basic Attack.png" data-image-key="Basic_Attack.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/c/cd/Basic_Attack.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20200517010633" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Damage" title="Damage">basic damage</a></span>, can <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Critical strike"><a href="/wiki/Critical_strike" title="Critical strike"><img alt="Critical strike icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Critical strike icon.png" data-image-key="Critical_strike_icon.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/41/Critical_strike_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20191126102550" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Critical_strike" title="Critical strike">critically strike</a></span> for <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions stunned with Pyromania (P)</span><span><span style="color:orange; white-space:normal">(82.<small>5</small>%&#160;+&#160;<span class="inline-image label-after item-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-item="Infinity Edge" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Infinity_Edge" title="38.5%"><img alt="38" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Infinity Edge item.png" data-image-key="Infinity_Edge_item.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/15/Infinity_Edge_item.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20201104234931" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Infinity_Edge" title="Infinity Edge">38.<small>5</small>%</a></span></span>) AD</span></span> <b>bonus</b> damage and apply <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="On-hit"><a href="/wiki/Attack_effects#On_Hitting" title="Attack effects"><img alt="On-hit icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="On-hit icon.png" data-image-key="On-hit_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/75/On-hit_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20201114055106" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Attack_effects#On_Hitting" title="Attack effects">on-hit</a></span> and <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="On-attack"><a href="/wiki/Attack_effects#On_Attacking" title="Attack effects">on-attack</a></span> effects at 100% effectiveness once on each target struck. <i>Burst Fire's</i> cooldown and cast time scale down with <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions hit with Martial Cadence (P)</span><span><span style="color: #F5EE99; white-space:normal">attack speed</span></span>, with the maximum of 1.<small>5</small> attacks per second. 50% of <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions hit with Martial Cadence (P)</span><span><span style="color: #F5EE99; white-space:normal">attack speed</span></span> in excess of the cap is converted into <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions hit with Bandage Toss (Q) at greater than 75% of max range</span><span><span style="color:orange; white-space:normal"><b>bonus</b> attack damage</span></span>.</li>
<li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Cost:</b></span> None</li>
<li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Cooldown:</b></span> (1/<b>Zeri's</b> <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions hit with Martial Cadence (P)</span><span><span style="color: #F5EE99; white-space:normal">attack speed</span></span>) seconds.</li>
<li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Range:</b></span> <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Cr"><a href="/wiki/Range" title="Range"><img alt="Range center" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Range center.png" data-image-key="Range_center.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/c/cf/Range_center.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20150616134211" class="lazyload" /></a></span> <span class="basic-tooltip" style="border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;" title="Active spray missile reaches">825</span>, <span class="template_sbc"><b>Width:</b></span> <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Er"><a href="/wiki/Range" title="Range"><img alt="Range model" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Range model.png" data-image-key="Range_model.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/71/Range_model.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20150616134216" class="lazyload" /></a></span> <span class="basic-tooltip" style="border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;" title="Active spray missiles">80</span>, <span class="template_sbc"><b>Speed:</b></span> <span class="basic-tooltip" style="border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;" title="Active spray missile speed">2600</span> / <span class="basic-tooltip" style="border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;" title="Empowered spray missile speed while Overcharged">3400</span>.</li></ul></li>
<li><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Ultrashock Laser" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Ultrashock_Laser" title="Ultrashock Laser"><img alt="Ultrashock Laser" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Ultrashock Laser.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Ultrashock_Laser.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/45/Zeri_Ultrashock_Laser.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813185815" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Ultrashock_Laser" title="Zeri/LoL">Ultrashock Laser</a></span></span> (W)
<ul><li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Active:</b></span> <b>Zeri</b> fires an electric pulse in the target direction that deals 40 / 75 / 110 / 145 / 180 <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions stunned with Pyromania (P)</span><span><span style="color:orange; white-space:normal">(+ 100% AD)</span></span> <span class="ll-item navbox">Multiple champions hit with Between Worlds (R)</span><span><span style="color: #7A6DFF; white-space:normal">(+ 60% AP)</span></span> <span class="ll-item navbox">Damage mitigated with Shifting Sands (E)</span><span><span style="color: #00B0F0; white-space:normal">magic damage</span></span> to the first enemy hit and <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Slow"><a href="/wiki/Slow" title="Slow"><img alt="Slow icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Slow icon.png" data-image-key="Slow_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/78/Slow_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20171201224744" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Slow" class="mw-redirect" title="Slow">slows</a></span> them by 50 / 55 / 60 / 65 / 70% for 1 / 1.<small>25</small> / 1.<small>5</small> / 1.<small>75</small> / 2 seconds. If the pulse collides with terrain, it transforms into a laser in a line from the point of impact that grants <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Sight"><a href="/wiki/Sight" title="Sight"><img alt="Sight icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Sight icon.png" data-image-key="Sight_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/0e/Sight_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20130928145820" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Sight" title="Sight">sight</a></span> of the area for 1.<small>75</small> seconds and fires after 0.<small>75</small> seconds, applying the same effects to all enemies caught within.</li>
<li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Mana Cost:</b></span> 50 / 60 / 70 / 80 / 90.</li>
<li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Cooldown:</b></span> 10 seconds.</li>
<li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Range:</b></span> <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Cr"><a href="/wiki/Range" title="Range"><img alt="Range center" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Range center.png" data-image-key="Range_center.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/c/cf/Range_center.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20150616134211" class="lazyload" /></a></span> <span class="basic-tooltip" style="border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;" title="Initial missile">1200</span> / <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Er"><a href="/wiki/Range" title="Range"><img alt="Range model" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Range model.png" data-image-key="Range_model.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/71/Range_model.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20150616134216" class="lazyload" /></a></span> <span class="basic-tooltip" style="border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;" title="Laser beam length">1500</span>, <span class="template_sbc"><b>Width:</b></span> <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Er"><a href="/wiki/Range" title="Range"><img alt="Range model" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Range model.png" data-image-key="Range_model.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/71/Range_model.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20150616134216" class="lazyload" /></a></span> <span class="basic-tooltip" style="border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;" title="Initial missile">80</span> / <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Er"><a href="/wiki/Range" title="Range"><img alt="Range model" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Range model.png" data-image-key="Range_model.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/71/Range_model.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20150616134216" class="lazyload" /></a></span> <span class="basic-tooltip" style="border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;" title="Laser beam width">200</span>, <span class="template_sbc"><b>Speed:</b></span> <span class="basic-tooltip" style="border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;" title="Initial missile">2200</span> / <span class="basic-tooltip" style="border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;" title="Laser beam">Instant</span>.</li></ul></li>
<li><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Spark Surge" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Spark_Surge" title="Spark Surge"><img alt="Spark Surge" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Spark Surge.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Spark_Surge.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/b/b7/Zeri_Spark_Surge.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813185756" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Spark_Surge" title="Zeri/LoL">Spark Surge</a></span></span> (E)
<ul><li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Active:</b></span> <b>Zeri</b> <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Dash"><a href="/wiki/Dash" title="Dash"><img alt="Dash" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Dash.png" data-image-key="Dash.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/55/Dash.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20180514002826" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Dash" title="Dash">dashes</a></span> in the target direction. Afterwards, she empowers her next 3 casts of <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Burst Fire 2" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire_2" title="Burst Fire"><img alt="Burst Fire" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Burst Fire 2.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Burst_Fire_2.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/df/Zeri_Burst_Fire_2.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20220108011904" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire_2" title="Zeri/LoL">Burst Fire</a></span></span> within 6 seconds, causing them to pierce through enemies, though dealing 80 / 85 / 90 / 95 / 100% damage after the first and not applying attack effects to secondary targets. This damage is affected by <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Critical strike"><a href="/wiki/Critical_strike" title="Critical strike"><img alt="Critical strike icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Critical strike icon.png" data-image-key="Critical_strike_icon.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/41/Critical_strike_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20191126102550" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Critical_strike" title="Critical strike">critical strike</a></span> modifiers.</li>
<li><b>Zeri</b> will dash farther across terrain if <i>Spark Surge</i> was cast within 50 units of any, gaining <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Unobstructed vision"><a href="/wiki/Sight#Unobstructed_vision" title="Sight"><img alt="Stealth Ward icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Stealth Ward icon.png" data-image-key="Stealth_Ward_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/b/b5/Stealth_Ward_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20171031100405" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Sight#Unobstructed_vision" title="Sight">unobstructed vision</a></span> of the surrounding 800 units and <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Sight"><a href="/wiki/Sight" title="Sight"><img alt="Sight icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Sight icon.png" data-image-key="Sight_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/0e/Sight_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20130928145820" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Sight" title="Sight">revealing</a></span> herself while there are enemy champions within 800 units of her.</li>
<li><i>Spark Surge's</i> cooldown is reduced by 1.<small>5</small> seconds for every champion <b>Zeri</b> hits with <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Basic Attack 2" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Basic_Attack_2" title="charged"><img alt="charged" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Living Battery 2.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Living_Battery_2.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/55/Zeri_Living_Battery_2.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20220108011853" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Basic_Attack_2" title="Zeri/LoL">charged</a></span></span> basic attacks or abilities.</li>
<li><i>Spark Surge</i> <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Basic attack reset"><a href="/wiki/Basic_attack#Resets" title="Basic attack"><img alt="Bladework" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Fiora Bladework.png" data-image-key="Fiora_Bladework.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/f/f4/Fiora_Bladework.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240812214631" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Basic_attack#Resets" title="Basic attack">resets</a></span> <b>Zeri's</b> basic attack timer and <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Burst Fire" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire" title="Burst Fire&#39;s"><img alt="Burst Fire&#39;s" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Burst Fire.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Burst_Fire.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/1e/Zeri_Burst_Fire.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813185727" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire" title="Zeri/LoL">Burst Fire's</a></span></span> cooldown. <b>Zeri</b> can cast <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Ultrashock Laser" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Ultrashock_Laser" title="Ultrashock Laser"><img alt="Ultrashock Laser" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Ultrashock Laser.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Ultrashock_Laser.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/45/Zeri_Ultrashock_Laser.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813185815" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Ultrashock_Laser" title="Zeri/LoL">Ultrashock Laser</a></span></span> and <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Lightning Crash" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Lightning_Crash" title="Lightning Crash"><img alt="Lightning Crash" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Lightning Crash.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Lightning_Crash.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/2/23/Zeri_Lightning_Crash.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813185746" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Lightning_Crash" title="Zeri/LoL">Lightning Crash</a></span></span> while <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Dash"><a href="/wiki/Dash" title="Dash"><img alt="Dash" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Dash.png" data-image-key="Dash.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/55/Dash.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20180514002826" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Dash" title="Dash">dashing</a></span>.</li>
<li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Mana Cost:</b></span> 80.</li>
<li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Cooldown:</b></span> <span class="basic-tooltip" style="border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;" title="Starts on-cast">23 / 21.<small>5</small> / 20 / 18.<small>5</small> / 17</span> seconds.</li>
<li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Range:</b></span> <span class="basic-tooltip" style="border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;" title="Standard dash distance">300</span>, <span class="template_sbc"><b>Speed:</b></span> 600 + <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions killed 5s before or after using Chronobreak (R)</span><span><span style="color: #FFFDC9; white-space:normal">100% movement speed</span></span>, <span class="template_sbc"><b>Cast Time:</b></span> None.</li></ul></li>
<li><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Lightning Crash" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Lightning_Crash" title="Lightning Crash"><img alt="Lightning Crash" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Lightning Crash.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Lightning_Crash.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/2/23/Zeri_Lightning_Crash.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813185746" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Lightning_Crash" title="Zeri/LoL">Lightning Crash</a></span></span> (R)
<ul><li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Active:</b></span> <b>Zeri</b> discharges a nova of electricity around her, dealing 150 / 250 / 350 <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions stunned with Pyromania (P)</span><span><span style="color:orange; white-space:normal">(+ 80% <b>bonus</b> AD)</span></span> <span class="ll-item navbox">Multiple champions hit with Between Worlds (R)</span><span><span style="color: #7A6DFF; white-space:normal">(+ 80% AP)</span></span> <span class="ll-item navbox">Damage mitigated with Shifting Sands (E)</span><span><span style="color: #00B0F0; white-space:normal">magic damage</span></span> to all nearby enemies.</li>
<li>If <i>Lightning Crash</i> hits at least one enemy champion, <b>Zeri</b> becomes <i>Overcharged</i> for 6 seconds, and gains 3 stacks of <i>Overcharge</i> per champion hit. Each stack grants her <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions killed 5s before or after using Chronobreak (R)</span><span><span style="color: #FFFDC9; white-space:normal">2% <b>bonus</b> movement speed</span></span>. She gains a stack of <i>Overcharge</i> each time she hits an enemy champion with a <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Basic Attack 2" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Basic_Attack_2" title="charged"><img alt="charged" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Living Battery 2.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Living_Battery_2.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/55/Zeri_Living_Battery_2.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20220108011853" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Basic_Attack_2" title="Zeri/LoL">charged</a></span></span> basic attack or ability, refreshing the duration of <i>Overcharge</i> by 2 seconds in the process.</li>
<li>While <i>Overcharged</i>, <b>Zeri</b> gains <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions hit with Martial Cadence (P)</span><span><span style="color: #F5EE99; white-space:normal">30 / 35 / 40% <b>bonus</b> attack speed</span></span> and deals <span class="ll-item navbox">Multiple champions hit with Between Worlds (R)</span><span><span style="color: #00B0F0; white-space:normal">10 / 20 / 30 <span class="ll-item navbox">Multiple champions hit with Between Worlds (R)</span><span><span style="color: #7A6DFF; white-space:normal">(+ 15% AP)</span></span> <b>bonus</b> magic damage</span></span> <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="On-hit"><a href="/wiki/Attack_effects#On_Hitting" title="Attack effects"><img alt="On-hit icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="On-hit icon.png" data-image-key="On-hit_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/75/On-hit_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20201114055106" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Attack_effects#On_Hitting" title="Attack effects">on-hit</a></span>, and empowers <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-ability="Burst Fire 3" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire_3" title="Burst Fire"><img alt="Burst Fire" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri Burst Fire 3.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Burst_Fire_3.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/de/Zeri_Burst_Fire_3.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20220108011914" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL#Burst_Fire_3" title="Zeri/LoL">Burst Fire</a></span></span> to instead fire 3 rounds over a 20% shorter cast time that are electrified and travelling with increased speed. These rounds deal the <span class="ll-item navbox">Damage mitigated with Shifting Sands (E)</span><span><span style="color: #00B0F0; white-space:normal"><b>bonus</b> magic damage</span></span> to the target struck and the closest <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Sight"><a href="/wiki/Sight" title="Sight"><img alt="Sight icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Sight icon.png" data-image-key="Sight_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/0e/Sight_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20130928145820" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Sight" title="Sight">visible</a></span> enemy, chaining up to 4 subsequent targets. Secondary targets are dealt <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions stunned with Pyromania (P)</span><span><span style="color:orange; white-space:normal">25% AD</span></span> <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions killed from outside standard Attack range</span><span><span style="color: #FF8C34; white-space:normal">physical damage</span></span>, which can <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Critical strike"><a href="/wiki/Critical_strike" title="Critical strike"><img alt="Critical strike icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Critical strike icon.png" data-image-key="Critical_strike_icon.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/41/Critical_strike_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20191126102550" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Critical_strike" title="Critical strike">critically strike</a></span> for <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions stunned with Pyromania (P)</span><span><span style="color:orange; white-space:normal">(43.<small>75</small>%&#160;+&#160;<span class="inline-image label-after item-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-item="Infinity Edge" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Infinity_Edge" title="18.375%"><img alt="18" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Infinity Edge item.png" data-image-key="Infinity_Edge_item.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/15/Infinity_Edge_item.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20201104234931" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Infinity_Edge" title="Infinity Edge">18.<small>375</small>%</a></span></span>) AD</span></span> <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions killed from outside standard Attack range</span><span><span style="color: #FF8C34; white-space:normal">physical damage</span></span>.</li>
<li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Mana Cost:</b></span> 100.</li>
<li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Cooldown:</b></span> <span class="basic-tooltip" style="border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;" title="Starts post-effect">100 / 90 / 80</span> seconds.</li>
<li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Effect Radius:</b></span> <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Cr"><a href="/wiki/Range" title="Range"><img alt="Range center" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Range center.png" data-image-key="Range_center.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/c/cf/Range_center.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20150616134211" class="lazyload" /></a></span> <span class="basic-tooltip" style="border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;" title="Nova radius">825</span>, <span class="template_sbc"><b>Cast Time:</b></span> 0.<small>25</small> seconds.</li></ul></li></ul></div>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Trivia">Trivia</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a title="Sign in to edit" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" data-tracking-label="log-in-edit-section" data-action="edit-section" href="https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fleagueoflegends.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FZeri%2FLoL%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D4&amp;uselang=en" data-testid="log-in-edit-section"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-pencil-tiny"></use></svg></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<ul><li>When <span class="inline-image label-after champion-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-skin="Original" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL" title="Zeri"><img alt="Zeri" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri OriginalSquare.png" data-image-key="Zeri_OriginalSquare.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/7d/Zeri_OriginalSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20220330171840" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><strong class="mw-selflink selflink">Zeri</strong></span></span> and <span class="inline-image label-after champion-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Ekko" data-skin="Original" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Ekko/LoL" title="Ekko"><img alt="Ekko" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Ekko OriginalSquare.png" data-image-key="Ekko_OriginalSquare.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/5f/Ekko_OriginalSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20151218185247" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Ekko/LoL" title="Ekko/LoL">Ekko</a></span></span> are on the same team, they gain a buff named <img alt="Zeri Ekko buff" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Zeri Ekko buff.png" data-image-key="Zeri_Ekko_buff.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/8/8c/Zeri_Ekko_buff.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20220108012156" class="lazyload" /> <i>Zaunite Ingenuity</i>, which reads <i>"Kids from the <span style="white-space:pre;"><a href="/wiki/Zaun" title="Zaun"><img alt="Zaun Crest icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="24" data-image-name="Zaun Crest icon.png" data-image-key="Zaun_Crest_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/9/93/Zaun_Crest_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20161117062823" class="lazyload" /></a> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Zaun" title="Zaun">undercity</a></span></span> stick together."</i></li>
<li><span class="inline-image label-after champion-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Zeri" data-skin="Original" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Zeri/LoL" title="Zeri"><img alt="Zeri" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Zeri OriginalSquare.png" data-image-key="Zeri_OriginalSquare.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/7d/Zeri_OriginalSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20220330171840" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><strong class="mw-selflink selflink">Zeri</strong></span></span>'s splash was different upon release. After a few days it was edited to show a darker skintone, smaller and more detailed eyes, among other changes. <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" class="external text" href="https://i.redd.it/sdrsel7taea81.gif">Gif comparison</a>.</li>
<li>She is the only champion with 0 point at a skill by the client classification.
<ul><li>In this case, her Utility rating is 0.</li></ul></li></ul>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="See_also">See also</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a title="Sign in to edit" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" data-tracking-label="log-in-edit-section" data-action="edit-section" href="https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fleagueoflegends.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FZeri%2FLoL%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D5&amp;uselang=en" data-testid="log-in-edit-section"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-pencil-tiny"></use></svg></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
